snippet.title: Baahubali - The Epic Release Trailer 2 (Telugu) | Prabhas, Rana | SS Rajamouli | 31st October 2025
snippet.description:
#BaahubaliTheEpic is a combined narrative of the two-part Indian film saga, weaving together the grandeur and drama of Baahubali: The Beginning and Baahubali: The Conclusion into one epic tale.

Worldwide Releasing On Oct 31st 2025.

CAST

Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW

Screenplay & Direction: S.S. Rajamouli

Here is the exclusive trailer of Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1, starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast. With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films.

Official Release Date October 31, 2025 in Kannada, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam on Prime Video India.

Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages ‚Äì including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. snippet.title: Peter (Kannada) - Teaser | Raajesh Dhruva | Janvi Rayala | Sukesh Shetty |¬†Vriddhi¬†Studios
snippet.description:
PETER is a dark and deeply emotional intense suspense¬†thriller where the line between love and vengeance fades in a world full of secrets. Directed and written by Sukesh Shetty, this film brings a unique cinematic style that blends intense action, heart-wrenching drama, and a powerful mystery at its core. The film is produced by Ravi Hiremath and Rakesh Heggade under the banner of Vriddhi Studios, delivering a grand cinematic experience designed for the big screen.

‚≠ê Starring the talented and dynamic Raajesh Dhruva, who steps into the role of Peter ‚Äî a man shaped by his past, broken by his present, and feared by those who know his name. His emotionally-driven performance stands at the center of this story. Janvi Rayala and Raviksha Shetty bring depth and grace to their roles, adding layers of compassion, strength, and emotional turmoil to the narrative.

The film features a strong supporting ensemble:
Ram Nadagoud, Varun Patel, Prathima Nayak, Raghu Pandeshwar, Radhakrishna Kumble, Deena Poojari, Siddu, Bharath, Manu Kasargod, Rakshit Doddera ‚Äî each delivering impactful performances that build the haunting world around Peter.

#Peter #PeterMovie #PeterKannadaMovie #KannadaMovie #Sandalwood #ActionThriller #MysteryThriller #NewKannadaMovie #2025KannadaMovies #RaajeshDhruva #SukeshShetty #VriddhiStudios #KannadaCinema #ComingSoon #MovieUpdate #teaser 

üé¨ A CINEMATIC EXPERIENCE FILLED WITH FEAR, HEART & COURAGE

This film invites the audience to walk a tightrope of suspense where every moment increases the tension.
It is not just a battle of fists ‚Äî it‚Äôs a battle of emotions.
Not just action ‚Äî but the weight of survival.

The story reveals a shocking truth buried deep within Peter‚Äôs life. What begins as a personal journey soon turns into a dangerous confrontation with the darkest side of humanity. Every choice he makes has consequences‚Ä¶ every silence hides a scream‚Ä¶ and every enemy he encounters brings him closer to the truth that can destroy him.

This is a film where mystery breathes, where pain speaks, and where a man fights ‚Äî not for victory, but for justice, love, and identity.

üé• TECHNICAL BRILLIANCE & CRAFTSMANSHIP

Writer & Director : Sukesh Shetty
Banner : Vriddhi Studios
Producer: Ravi Hiremath, Rakesh Heggade

üéµ Music ‚Äì Ritviik Muralidhar
A stunning musical score that amplifies fear, emotion, and adrenaline. The songs craft memories, while the BGM raises the intensity with every pulse.
‚úÇÔ∏è Editor ‚Äì Naveen Shetty
Provides a crisp, gripping narrative where every scene and transition builds suspense ‚Äî ensuring the thriller never loses pace.
üé¨ Teaser Editor ‚Äì Aldren Jude

en-IN.description:
PETER is a dark and deeply emotional intense suspense¬†thriller where the line between love and vengeance fades in a world full of secrets. Directed and written by Sukesh Shetty, this film brings a unique cinematic style that blends intense action, heart-wrenching drama, and a powerful mystery at its core. The film is produced by Ravi Hiremath and Rakesh Heggade under the banner of Vriddhi Studios, delivering a grand cinematic experience designed for the big screen.

‚≠ê Starring the talented and dynamic Raajesh Dhruva, who steps into the role of Peter ‚Äî a man shaped by his past, broken by his present, and feared by those who know his name. His emotionally-driven performance stands at the center of this story. Janvi Rayala and Raviksha Shetty bring depth and grace to their roles, adding layers of compassion, strength, and emotional turmoil to the narrative.

The film features a strong supporting ensemble:
Ram Nadagoud, Varun Patel, Prathima Nayak, Raghu Pandeshwar, Radhakrishna Kumble, Deena Poojari, Siddu, Bharath, Manu Kasargod, Rakshit Doddera ‚Äî each delivering impactful performances that build the haunting world around Peter.

snippet.title: Creedence Clearwater Revival - Have You Ever Seen The Rain (Fan Celebration Version)
snippet.description:
We are celebrating your comments for the official Have You Ever Seen The Rain music video. Thank you for supporting CCR! 

About Creedence Clearwater Revival: 
Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs 1968 self-titled debut album introduced the world to guitar-playing brothers John and Tom‚ÄØFogerty, drummer Doug Clifford, and bassist Stu Cook, four young men out of El Cerrito in the San Francisco Bay Area. Though they emerged in a place and time where trippy psychedelic visions were the order of‚ÄØthe day, CCR bucked the trends and instead tapped into a rich, traditional seam of American music that connected to blues, country, rockabilly, gospel, folk and R&B.‚ÄØ‚ÄØ‚ÄØ 

During their short time together as a band (1968 ‚Äì 1972), the band enjoyed an unparalleled period of creativity lead by singer, songwriter, arranger John Fogerty. They‚Äôve sold close to 100 million records, releasing 14 Top 10 hits. They also managed to play over 150 tour dates around the world, including a headlining spot at Woodstock.

Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs canon has become a part of the Great American Songbook. Fogerty penned songs like ‚ÄúBad Moon Rising,‚Äù ‚ÄúDown on the Corner,‚Äù ‚ÄúFortunate Son,‚Äù ‚ÄúHave You Ever Seen the Rain,‚Äù ‚ÄúProud Mary,‚Äù ‚ÄúBorn on the Bayou,‚Äù ‚ÄúTravelin‚Äô Band‚Äù and ‚ÄúUp Around the Bend‚Äù have been ingrained into pop culture ‚Äî not just as rock staples, but as classic standards.

With so many memorable songs that continue to grace our radio waves, television and movie screens, plus lyrics that still resonate today, Creedence Clearwater Revival is, truly, America‚Äôs greatest rock ‚Äôn‚Äô roll band.

snippet.description:
‚ÄúAa Bhi Ja Aa Bhi Ja‚Äù is a soulful and evocative ballad featured in the 2002 musical drama Sur ‚Äì The Melody of Life, starring Lucky Ali alongside Gauri Karnik. Sung with heartfelt emotion by Lucky Ali and Sunidhi Chauhan,  

#AaBhiJaAaBhiJa #SurTheMelodyOfLife #LuckyAli #GauriKarnik #SunidhiChauhan #BollywoodClassics #EvergreenSongs #Bollywood #RomanticBallad 

Credits: 
Singer: Lucky Ali, Sunidhi Chauhan
Music: M.M. Kareem 
Lyrics: Nida Fazli
Movie: Sur The Melody Of Life
Starring: Lucky Ali, Gauri Karnik
Director: Tanuja Chandra
Producer: Fish Eye Network
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics:  
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
Raat Ko Kar Vida, Dilruba Aa Bhi Jaa ... 
 
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
  
Raat Ko Kar Vida, Dilruba Aa Bhi Jaa ... 
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa 
Mere, Mere Dil Ke Paagalpan Ki Oh Seema Kya Hai 
  
Yun To Tu Hai Meri, Chhaaya Tujh Mein, Ho, Tera Kya Hai 
Main Hoon Gagan Tu Hai Zameen, Adhoori Si Mere Bina
Raat Ko Kar Vida, Dilruba Aa Bhi Jaa 
  
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa... 
 
Dekhoon Chaahe Jisko, Kuch Kuch Tujhsa Dikhta Kyon Hai 
Jaano, Jaano Na Main, Tera Mera Rishta Kyon Hai 
Kaise Kahoon Kitna Bechain Hai Dil Mera Tere Bina 
Raat Ko Kar Vida, Dilruba Aa Bhi Jaa ... 
  
Aa Bhi Jaa, Aa Bhi Jaa, Ae Subaah Aa Bhi Jaa...
